Package com.stuypulse.stuylib.math

Class Vector3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stuypulse.stuylib.math.Vector3D
  • public final class Vector3D
extends java.lang.Object
    A Vector3D class that stores x, y, and z position data. It is made to work with the StuyLib Angle class and be easy to use. It is a standard Vector3D class with all of the functions that you would expect.
